{"tid":1468484,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［一句到尾］係香港人想贏就團結，不分化不割","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T18:42:27.000Z","uid":65213,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6da18c9eb71c7fd38a19789b7f86c5ee6ae92f80","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"依家香港需要的唔係指責<br />\n<br />\n係團結呀！係正能量呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要罵可以，要屌都可以，要割都可以<br />\n<br />\n但唔該係完左場仗先好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">輸左一次2014，係未想輸多次2019？</span><br />\n<br />\n當有問題出現果陣，覺得絕望果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好好諗下點解我地當初要企出來<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P4aMkyBqI5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP4aMkyBqI5A&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=c048becd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P4aMkyBqI5A</a><br />\n<br />\n借HOCC首歌打打氣"},{"pid":"bdc861224b9ffc9c5202dc91a1c9bc5f100c64f2","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:58:42.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"01f39ad7e71ab59efe921207359cea3719aee675","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:08.000Z","msg":"唔想見到明天又為左昨天互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966f07023145533a06ca930e688fa2a3a52a96cd","tid":1468484,"uid":234352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n求下大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其諗塞機場對錯，不如諗8.16㩒錢經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3iOuw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3iOuw0.png&h=d9b01fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJHSWb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJHSWb0.png&h=a04d9291&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZxSWb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZxSWb1.jpg&h=503ace62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd7a3e94f8536863565aeb60fd9b9820b5badf55","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"推比更多人睇"},{"pid":"f355223d9814f28ea437eeb990b81888a917dbed","tid":1468484,"uid":30697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:14.000Z","msg":"#我係禮貌撚<br />\n#我係道歉撚 #代香港政府道歉 #要抗爭 撳錢就得<br />\n<br />\n[幫推]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1</a><br />\n&quot;對唔住呀，我地個政府好撚衰，我代佢道歉&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1</a><br />\n對政府不合作 唔係對市民不合作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球道歉運動! <br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nSay 句 Sorry, 好易啫 ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#團結! Be water! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!<br />\n#816轉美元!<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！<br />\n#絕不割蓆，唯要改進"},{"pid":"5d6aca4042edef9914967b78fb4c20f909e64df4","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedb9251daa6d6b27dd42d4c6d154d7dae0e7de0","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:57.000Z","msg":"互相支持比互屌有用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55423d33164a20210153b7b7e7cfcad1c9869e59","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56a367c053a4978bde233d44af36434aeef9d4da","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"香港人加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f31d367d3db4077b1c6d4d416727f0e34bebf5","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3419580810f6af7e1322979aa037ccd27ff8a607","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"無曬巴絲？"},{"pid":"7141dfe0e407ba5c1a0d313bb0c0304f735b31d4","tid":1468484,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88a3d9785b9fd3558d7873cd3c13fdd22b55ec75","tid":1468484,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"第一句就 &quot;她的臉沒了&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年前既歌仲可以套用係而家既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231fd54b29b92e6c6fe19ef3a11dd82e1bad95d4","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"不氣餒要加油！"},{"pid":"52749d8b1b5c187acf71435738a8f29feb90a3dd","tid":1468484,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4918360734ae9958699bbb5a3870da0942c7900e","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"818要企出來！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28722ef6e6e7699258c8841a2a0848876e93827","tid":1468484,"uid":292668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b21a445fbea5576daf1b13d9e3c3f3dec6c2da8","tid":1468484,"uid":288786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"時代革命第二波--經濟上打敗親共財團<br />\n<br />\n真香港人在2019年6月開始的大時代付出了大量傷痛、血汗和生命代價，令自由世界的人民領略到真香港人對抗中共港共的不公義的無比勇敢與極高智慧，全世界都肯定真香港人是最偉大的民族之一。中共的卑劣手段及與民為敵惡魔本性令真香港人更堅定雙普選及民族自決才是未來的出路。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們應該進入下一波時代革命：在經濟上趕走親共財團與用貪腐養大的中聯辦（至少要他們減血九成），這些官商勾結財團是會牢牢掌握佢地嘅不公義制度。我們應該建立抗共經濟，區別於親共財團，我們要通過與歐美的聯繫說服歐美（包括香港人權法等等方式）制裁香港的親共財團的出口及其他經濟活動，同時保持讓真香港人的抗共經濟保持免稅、免制裁優惠。<br />\n<br />\n我們絕對可以在這個全球經濟轉型時創造奇蹟，理由如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.香港人的經濟活力、專業精神、全球網絡非常適合industry 4.0及因中美貿易戰需重建的供應鏈，我們可以建立flexible workshop同技術為本製造靈活的訂單；<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港在90年代有大量的工業技術人才，我們可以利用網絡聯繫重啟他們的技術talent (例如在連登中發表「職得做xxx的入黎」，我們可以製造出比淘寶優質的產品，真香港人現正開始大量參與使用及研發人工智能可以擴展我們的生產能力千倍或萬倍，因此我們可以製造出與淘寶一樣versatile 豐富多彩的產品系列 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/08/12/why-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40/amp/；\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjanakirammsv%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2Fwhy-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40%2Famp%2F%EF%BC%9B&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=381d7511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/08/12/why-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40/amp/；</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 有足夠的香港及海外資金願意投資香港的抗共經濟，尤其是建立的人網絡為產品增值，industry 4.0的產品可以由全球供應鏈合作而成，真香港人正是適合在其中扮演agents；<br />\n<br />\n4. 抗共經濟可以在香港本土迅速成長，我們可以借助文宣的經驗說服香港人大量購買使用抗共經濟的產品；<br />\n<br />\n5.可以考慮用非牟利捐款形式開始智囊及商會，團結越多人越成功，協調logistics 也是真香港人能夠做得最好的。商會也要分辨是否有親中商人混入真香港人經濟圈；<br />\n<br />\n6.真香港人投入新經濟一定會得到全世界的支持，因為industry 4.0正是需要真香港人的特質作為領頭羊，而不是中共貪腐結構下的工業人。不可否認，中國的industry 4.0是相當領先，但他們搞的并非歐美期望的將部分workshop留在歐美(global players,regional segmentation)，真香港人就可以做得到 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/independenttelegraph.com/big-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar/10793/amp/;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Findependenttelegraph.com%2Fbig-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar%2F10793%2Famp%2F%3B&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=219f9780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/independenttelegraph.com/big-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar/10793/amp/;</a><br />\n<br />\n7. 要達到經濟獨立并最終令中共給予真香港人雙普選，我們仍然要間中用抗爭用選票打低親中建制，但請真香港人be water，盡量不要流血或被捕。<br />\n<br />\n本人上述建議只是拋磚引玉，請更多專家們為抗共自主經濟出謀劃策。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"749eb5ca70fc8b80eb718ffaf659c126004d170a","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMv5DKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMv5DKs.jpg&h=08aa3cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59bcad9c87b19f36d953381ae160833a3fa35e26","tid":1468484,"uid":224716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門] <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">核彈都唔割嘅真正原因</span></span><br />\n入黎睇下啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEtzAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEtzAS</a><br />\n一齊加油啊"},{"pid":"7e80eda293fdffae1e3ec8a1109343303d0666cb","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"非推不可"},{"pid":"4f8625d203b53430fa94301588106f09ddd5ead0","tid":1468484,"uid":71997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:34:46.000Z","msg":"成個連登都互𨳒架啦，講乜𨶙都有人𨳒"},{"pid":"9bbdf43cd7530e66b4d940165a39aaf9f7087850","tid":1468484,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"818 一定要出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a897a21af481a264aeb1a5f58233456ae6d518be","tid":1468484,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推到核爆</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推到核爆</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推到核爆</span></strong></span>"}]}